{"tid":580761,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"希汀克執掌車路士直至季尾","createTime":"2018-03-04T18:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T18:12:58.000Z","uid":57035,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"da9dbe1d4108161ebaa1d32e284d3689aac94ef3","tid":580761,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:09:12.000Z","msg":"英超球會車路士宣布，委任荷蘭教練希汀克出任領隊直至季尾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2015/12/20151219_SP_%E5%B8%8C%E6%B1%80%E5%85%8B_01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2015%2F12%2F20151219_SP_%25E5%25B8%258C%25E6%25B1%2580%25E5%2585%258B_01.jpg&h=3806d251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英超球會車路士今晚在聯賽，主場迎戰新特蘭前，宣布委任69歲的荷蘭教練希汀克暫代領隊，直至季尾。車路士在聲明中讚揚希汀克是一位經驗豐富的領隊，又指班主艾巴莫域治相信他可以發揮球隊最大的潛力。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n2009年車路士辭退的巴西領隊史高拉利後，亦曾委任軒迪克「上車」擔任看守領隊至球季完結，即年就帶領球隊取得足總盃冠軍。"},{"pid":"5d9aa8c1f47cd125dbd199e64af9034b1c7ec7db","tid":580761,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:11:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb4a0e9f99d3be8145d937a3bae1e5e74987b3eb","tid":580761,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d9aa8c1f47cd125dbd199e64af9034b1c7ec7db","tid":580761,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:11:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:12:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nIs so Exciting 呀"}]}